You can explore your data without loading it into CRM Analytics or preparing it in datasets. CRM Analytics Direct Data lets you analyze and explore your data that resides in Salesforce objects, CDP, Snowflake, and Google BigQuery. You can run queries on the data in real time and also build dashboard widgets based on the queries you run.

Unlock CRM Analytics Insights on Data Cloud
Analyze your unified customer info in Data Cloud. With CRM Analytics Direct Data for Data Cloud, you can operationalize data analysis without first loading Data Cloud, prepping it, or creating live datasets. Embed Data Cloud records into CRM Analytics dashboards for any Salesforce object and run queries on the data in real time using single sign-on across both platforms.

Gain Insights on Data Directly in Snowflake
You can explore your data in a Snowflake warehouse without loading data into CRM Analytics or preparing it in datasets. CRM Analytics Direct Data for Snowflake lets you set up a live connection to the Snowflake schema you want to explore.

Gain Insights on Data Directly in Google BigQuery
You can explore your data in a Google BigQuery data warehouse without loading data into CRM Analytics or preparing it in datasets. CRM Analytics Direct Data for Google BigQuery lets you set up a live connection to the BigQuery schema you want to explore.
